//program-think.blogspot.com/2013/12/weekly-share-61.html?showComment=1387377019722#c7413358637904724341","title":"每周转载&#65306;网友热议北朝鲜张成泽倒台"},{"rel":"related","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/3973740093594491278/comments/default/2206051078235766821?v=2"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg?cache=36c4cca294ae50025f1c139a5907df5d"}}],"thr$in-reply-to":{"xmlns$thr":"http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2013/12/weekly-share-61.html","ref":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-3973740093594491278","source":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/3973740093594491278","type":"text/html"},"gd$extendedProperty":[{"name":"blogger.itemClass","value":"pid-1582521586"},{"name":"blogger.displayTime","value":"2013年12月18日 22:30:00"}]},{"gd$etag":"W/\"CUQCSXw_cSp7ImA9XRJWEko.\"","id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-4734790788931954158"},"published":{"$t":"2015-10-20T00:49:28.249+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2015-10-20T00:49:28.249+08:00"},"app$edited":{"xmlns$app":"http://www.w3.org/2007/app","$t":"2015-10-20T00:49:28.249+08:00"},"title":{"$t":"TO 基尔霍夫\n多谢老熟人捧场 :)"},"content":{"type":"html","$t":"TO 基尔霍夫<br />多谢老熟人捧场 :)"},"link":[{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/6410161999659956538/comments/default/4734790788931954158?v=2"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/6410161999659956538/comments/default/4734790788931954158?v=2"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2015/10/What-is-Science.html?showComment=1445273368249#c4734790788931954158","title":"科学是什么&#65311;&#8212;&#8212;兼谈&#8220;非科学&#12289;伪科学&#12289;反科学&#8221;和一些常见谬误"},{"rel":"related","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/6410161999659956538/comments/default/669079809172649642?v=2"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg?cache=36c4cca294ae50025f1c139a5907df5d"}}],"thr$in-reply-to":{"xmlns$thr":"http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2015/10/What-is-Science.html","ref":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-6410161999659956538","source":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/6410161999659956538","type":"text/html"},"gd$extendedProperty":[{"name":"blogger.itemClass","value":"pid-1582521586"},{"name":"blogger.displayTime","value":"2015年10月20日 00:49:00"}]},{"gd$etag":"W/\"CUQDRHo5cSp7ImA9XBJbEEs.\"","id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1968471438873933841"},"published":{"$t":"2019-01-21T17:36:15.429+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2019-01-21T17:36:15.429+08:00"},"app$edited":{"xmlns$app":"http://www.w3.org/2007/app","$t":"2019-01-21T17:36:15.429+08:00"},"title":{"$t":"TO 29楼的网友\n首先，非常感谢给俺提建议 :)\n针对你提到的几点，俺逐一回复如下：\n\n1、白名单..."},"content":{"type":"html","$t":"TO 29楼的网友<br />首先，非常感谢给俺提建议 :)<br />针对你提到的几点，俺逐一回复如下：<br /><br />1、白名单模式<br />白名单模式，如果基于【登录用户】，应该是没啥问题。<br />但如果基于【匿名用户】，可能比较难操作。<br />因为匿名用户存在【冒名顶替】的情况（很多职业五毛喜欢这么干）。<br />所以针对【匿名用户】的用户名设置白名单，效果未必好。<br /><br />2、身份验证机制<br />理论上可以提供某种基于【公钥机制】的身份验证，给匿名用户使用。<br />但在操作上会比较繁琐，而且很多用户是不太懂技术，可能搞不明白如何操作<br /><br />3、热度算法<br />最近半年，俺已经调整过热度算法。<br />主要是针对某些匿名用户“刷热度”的情况。<br />同时也加大了【登录用户】的权重——因为登录用户【不】存在冒名顶替，“身份可信度”比匿名用户更高。<br /><br />小结<br />关于上述这3条，俺可能会优先考虑【热度算法】。<br />因为这种方式对读者而言是【透明】滴——不会改变现有的界面和留言方式"},"link":[{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2053489966989372984/comments/default/1968471438873933841?v=2"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2053489966989372984/comments/default/1968471438873933841?v=2"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/01/ten-years-blogging.html?showComment=1548063375429#c1968471438873933841","title":"开博十周年庆&#65292;博文分类汇总"},{"rel":"related","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2053489966989372984/comments/default/4987633629402204477?v=2"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg?cache=36c4cca294ae50025f1c139a5907df5d"}}],"thr$in-reply-to":{"xmlns$thr":"http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/01/ten-years-blogging.html","ref":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-2053489966989372984","source":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/2053489966989372984","type":"text/html"},"gd$extendedProperty":[{"name":"blogger.itemClass","value":"pid-1582521586"},{"name":"blogger.displayTime","value":"2019年1月21日 17:36:00"}]},{"gd$etag":"W/\"CkQCQX4-cCp7ImA9WhBaF0g.\"","id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-5180674381491994759"},"published":{"$t":"2013-05-28T22:12:40.058+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2013-05-28T22:12:40.058+08:00"},"app$edited":{"xmlns$app":"http://www.w3.org/2007/app","$t":"2013-05-28T22:12:40.058+08:00"},"title":{"$t":"TO 6楼\n多谢分享维基百科链接 :)\n\nTO 1单元\n俺之前有介绍过，把压缩文件伪装成图片。\n但那..."},"content":{"type":"html","$t":"TO 6楼<br />多谢分享维基百科链接 :)<br /><br />TO 1单元<br />俺之前有介绍过，把压缩文件伪装成图片。<br />但那时用在特殊场合。<br />对于俺共享的电子书，如果这么干，会增加大伙儿的麻烦。<br /><br />TO 2单元<br />GDrive 的这个特性，貌似用不到。<br />因为俺网盘主要用来分享电子书，而不是文字文档。<br /><br />TO 3单元<br />多谢提醒 Dropbox 的安全性。<br />安全性不够强算是 Dropbox 的一个缺点。"},"link":[{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4586802057678147441/comments/default/5180674381491994759?v=2"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4586802057678147441/comments/default/5180674381491994759?v=2"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2013/05/share-polity-books.html?showComment=1369750360058#c5180674381491994759","title":"分享政治类电子书&#65288;30本&#65289;&#8212;&#8212;另征求&#8220;第2网盘&#8221;的建议"},{"rel":"related","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4586802057678147441/comments/default/5531553859733081157?v=2"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg?cache=36c4cca294ae50025f1c139a5907df5d"}}],"thr$in-reply-to":{"xmlns$thr":"http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2013/05/share-polity-books.html","ref":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-4586802057678147441","source":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/4586802057678147441","type":"text/html"},"gd$extendedProperty":[{"name":"blogger.itemClass","value":"pid-1582521586"},{"name":"blogger.displayTime","value":"2013年5月28日 22:12:00"}]},{"gd$etag":"W/\"CUQBQHwyfyp7ImA9XBJbGUg.\"","id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1282933936027329369"},"published":{"$t":"2019-02-01T00:49:11.297+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2019-02-01T00:49:11.297+08:00"},"app$edited":{"xmlns$app":"http://www.w3.org/2007/app","$t":"2019-02-01T00:49:11.297+08:00"},"title":{"$t":"TO 挪威森林猫\n多谢老熟人捧场 :)\n\n前几天说到的 FAQ，俺也在构思。\n这玩意儿比较难弄 :(..."},"content":{"type":"html","$t":"TO 挪威森林猫<br />多谢老熟人捧场 :)<br /><br />前几天说到的 FAQ，俺也在构思。<br />这玩意儿比较难弄 :(<br /><br />关于你提到的几点，俺逐一回复如下：<br /><br />1、<br />俺已经在“社会工程学”那个章节加了“信任”的小节<br /><br />2、<br />举个例子：<br />俺日常跟同事聊的话题，与俺博客上聊的话题，重叠度比较低，但又不为零。<br />重叠度太高，会引起怀疑；完全不重叠，也会引起怀疑 :)<br /><br />3、<br />这个做法，在【隐匿性】方面，效果【不】明显。<br />对于 ISP 那端，每一次重新分配的 IP，肯定会记录：新的公网 IP、宽带用户标识、时间<br />所以你即便频繁切换，只要公网 IP 暴露过一次，就【有可能】被关联到【宽带用户标识】<br />之前俺在某篇翻墙的博文中聊过这招。当时是为了【翻墙】的效果，与隐匿性无关。<br /><br />4、<br />这个就不好说了。不同的人，成本不同。<br />御用骇客的成本高，不会老是盯着俺（但俺要始终保持小心）<br />五毛水军的成本低，肯定会长期来评论区捣乱（俺反正也习惯了，不受影响）<br /><br />5、<br />俺倒是想起一个类似的——<br />对“网监部门的态度”，既不要把他们当白痴，也不要以为他们是万能的。"},"link":[{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2897277223911398654/comments/default/1282933936027329369?v=2"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2897277223911398654/comments/default/1282933936027329369?v=2"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/01/Security-Guide-for-Political-Activists.html?showComment=1548953351297#c1282933936027329369","title":"为啥朝廷总抓不到俺&#8212;&#8212;十年反党活动的安全经验汇总"},{"rel":"related","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2897277223911398654/comments/default/6687848892375876787?v=2"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAA